title: Mozart - Piano Concerto No. 12 (arr. Mozart), Piano Quartet No.
description:
Mozart:

I. Piano Concerto No. 12, K414 (arr. Mozart for piano and string quartet),
II. Piano Quartet No. 2, K493.

Mozart's arrangement of his Piano Concerto No. 12 effectively turns a piano concerto into a piano quintet! Both of these pieces were recorded live in 1999 by Alfred Brendel (piano) and the Alban Berg Quartet. They were released by EMI the following year.

Please enjoy.
